all-packages.description:
			The &lt;b&gt;as3-universal-analytics&lt;/b&gt; library.&lt;br&gt;
			&lt;br&gt;
			An ActionScript 3.0 implementation of the Google Analytics &lt;a href="http://developers.google.com/analytics/devguides/collection/protocol/v1/"&gt;Measurement Protocol&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;
			which allow you to:
			&lt;ul&gt;
				&lt;li&gt;
				Measure user activity in new environments.
				&lt;li&gt;
				Tie online to offline behavior.
				&lt;/li&gt;
				&lt;li&gt;
				Send data from both the client and server.
				&lt;/li&gt;
			&lt;/ul>

			We support 3 runtimes:
			&lt;ul&gt;
				&lt;li&gt;
				Flash Player plugin&lt;br&gt;
                to track on the &lt;b&gt;browser&lt;/b&gt;
                &lt;br&gt;
                &lt;a href="http://github.com/zwetan/as3-universal-analytics/wiki/trackWithFlash" target="_blank"&gt;Tracking with Flash Player plugin&lt;/a&gt;
				&lt;/li&gt;
				&lt;li&gt;
				AIR (Adobe Integrated Runtime)&lt;br&gt;
				to track on &lt;b&gt;desktop&lt;/b&gt; and &lt;b&gt;mobile&lt;/b&gt; applications
                &lt;br&gt;
                &lt;a href="http://github.com/zwetan/as3-universal-analytics/wiki/trackWithAIR" target="_blank"&gt;Tracking with AIR&lt;/a&gt;
				&lt;/li&gt;
				&lt;li&gt;
				Redtamarin&lt;br&gt;
				to track on the &lt;b&gt;command-line&lt;/b&gt; and &lt;b&gt;server side&lt;/b&gt;
                &lt;br&gt;
                &lt;a href="http://github.com/zwetan/as3-universal-analytics/wiki/trackWithRedtamarin" target="_blank"&gt;Tracking with Redtamarin&lt;/a&gt;
				&lt;/li&gt;
			&lt;/ul>

			&lt;a href="https://github.com/zwetan/as3-universal-analytics/wiki" target="_blank"&gt;Wiki Documentation&lt;/a&gt;

package.description:
Part of the Portable Operating System Interface library,
the library provides access to the POSIX operating system API.&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
see: &lt;a href="http://pubs.opengroup.org/onlinepubs/9699919799/basedefs/unistd.h.html" target="_blank"&gt;Opengroup unistd.h&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
see: &lt;a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Unistd.h" target="_blank"&gt;Wikipedia unistd.h&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;b&gt;Redtamarin only&lt;/b&gt;

The cryptography library (or &lt;b&gt;cryptolib&lt;/b&gt;) contains classes, functions
and other definitions that implement various ciphers, hashes, public-key
and symmetric-key algorithms.
